    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">I joined AstraZeneca last year as a Machine Learning Engineer within the BIKG team. Our team is a group of talented people with a variety of skill sets. My academic background is in Computer Science with industry experience in Data Science and Cyber Security. I am currently developing the machine learning models that exploit our knowledge graph.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">We have many exciting opportunities available at AstraZeneca, and we are always on the lookout for talented people. If you are interested in joining us, why not take a look at our <a href="https://careers.astrazeneca.com/" target="_self">current vacancies</a>?</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
